summary: Rings of Effects adds 4 effects to your character to make your Dovakiin even more Epic!
descriptionHtml:
Rings of Effects adds 4 effects to your character to make your Dovakiin even more Epic!

This mods adds four new rings to be worn and make your character look really cool!

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Hey Guys,  you can head to the URL down Below to see some upcoming mods that I\'m making.

[http://267mods.tumblr.com/]
-------------------------------------------
Rings:
Fire Effect
Frost Effect
Nature Effect
Night Mare Effect
-------------------------------------------
Each ring has been balanced and price correctly.

Each ring also has some hidden effects to make your character stronger!
-------------------------------------------
Where can the rings be found?

They can be bought off of the court wizard in White Run Dragon Search.
-------------------------------------------
Please support this mod by Endorsing if you enjoy!

For up coming things, you can follow me on twitter <@Bill267Mods>  

If there are any bugs, or comments, please comment, or feel free to email me at <bill267mods@gmail.com>
